OL,4,G1540FCome Dine with Me
OL,5,     GKent. Photographer Anthony plans
OL,6,     Gto impress his guests with
OL,7,     Gculinary excellence on the final
OL,8,     Gnight. Mark's on cheesy
OL,9,     Goverdrive, and Karen showcases
OL,10,     Gsome incredible impressions.
OL,11,G1615FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GJane and Keith Smith welcome
OL,13,     Gtheir rivals to the Swallows Rest
OL,14,     Gin Weymouth, Dorset. But some of
OL,15,     GJane's colour combinations don't
OL,16,     Ggo down well with one guest.
